        "Description": "47, our client forgot to book a reservation to the Barbiae movie premiere, and he absolutely doesnt want to miss a single second. By the time he arrives, he wants the receptionist out of the way, and for you to leave the area, for it would &quot;Ruin the vibe of Barbiae.&quot;. Also they want him sniped because &quot;Why not.&quot;. You cannot be spotted 47.  I will leave you to prepare.",
